</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-CONFESSES-BOOK-PART1-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CHELSEA'S ROCKY ROAD TO THE WHITE HOUSE; BILL'S CONFESSION  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
   (PLEASE NOTE: The following book excerpt _ one of three from the
