 &HT;    Amid reports of oral sex in the Oval Office and Monica
Lewinsky's semen-stained blue Gap dress that surfaced in July,
Chelsea sided with her mother. And like the first lady, Chelsea now
refused to speak to her father at all.
 &HT;    .....
 &HT;    On Aug. 13, a Thursday, Bill made the long and lonely journey
from the Oval Office to Hillary's bedroom. There was no longer any
