</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PILGRIM CHURCH HAS CHANGED, BUT PRINCIPLES REMAIN
 &HT;    With MILLENNIUM-OVERVIEW, MILLENNIUM-CATHOLIC AND
MILLENNIUM-BLACK.
 &HT;    Moving in (a) national and (l) lifestyle categories for release
Sunday, Aug. 22.
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WEST BARNSTABLE, Mass. _ From the high pulpit, the Rev. Reed
Baer gazes down upon a congregation with a lineage beginning before
