<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CHALLENGE-FOR-HACKERS-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HACK IT IF YOU CAN  
 (FOR RELEASE THE WEEK OF MON., AUG. 16, 1999)
</HEADLINE>
   (This article from the London-based science and technology weekly
