 Friday, Aug. 13, 1999    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file or has filed the
following for Saturday and Sunday. If you have questions, please
call Chuck Lewis or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about
Houston Chronicle sports stories, please call 713-220-7896.
