   FBC-GAMECOCKS _ COLUMBIA S.C . _ The AJC's preseason Road to
College Football travels to South Carolina. Veteran coach Lou Holtz
has brought a high level of excitement to the program, but will it
translate to victories on the field? (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) 20.
</P>
<P>
   TENNIS
</P>
<P>
   GRAF-RETIRES _ There will be no farewell tour for Steffi Graf,
one of the greatest women's players ever. Graf, who announced her
immediate retirement Friday morning, used her powerful forehand
shots to win 22 Grand Slam singles titles _ second only to Margaret
Court's 24 _ and 107 tournaments on the WTA Tour. (Holcomb, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
<P>
   STEFFI _ WEST PLAM BEACH _ Steffi Graf retires from tennis.
Mainbar. (Clarke, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
