<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Turner Broadcasting delays launch of women-oriented cable
channel
 &HT;    By Charles Haddad
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ It's been a busy year for Turner Broadcasting. So
busy, in fact, that the Atlanta-based cable TV programmer has
decided to scale back ambitious plans to launch three new channels
within the next year.
