<P>
   IRIDIUM-BANKRUPTCY (Chicago) _ Just eight months after it
started an ambitious satellite telephone service that promised to
communicate ``with anyone, anytime, virtually anywhere in the
world,'' Iridium LLC has filed for bankruptcy protection. By David
Barboza.
</P>
<P>
   (The story is scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
