<P>
   BC-CNN-WILLOW-BAY-NYT (moved on Friday, Aug. 6)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Friday, Aug. 6,
about the new anchors for the CNN business-news program ``Moneyline
News Hour'' misstated the year that both CNN and the program were
founded. It was 1980, not 1984.
