<P>
   &QL; 
 &LR;  &QR; 
 &UR; LEVIS  &LR; _ The San Francisco jeansmaker is opening a flagship store
at Union Square this week. Over the years the company's experience
in retailing has been a downer. In its latest effort Levi's is
trying to use the new store as a branding mechanism to appeal to
youth. The store will feature stuff like like a DJ table, various
tie-ins to rock music sponsorships, unusual fashions, a
custom-tailoring department, etc. By Carol Emert
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-08-13-99 2230EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
